@startuml

title Solid\nOpenID Connect (OIDC)\nAuthorization Code Flow - Example 1

!include_once actors.puml

== Flows ==

alt User provides WebID
group Fetch WebID Profile (Example 1)
    autonumber 1.1
    user o-> app: Provide WebID URL
    activate app
        app -> solid.idp: Request WebID URL

        activate solid.idp
            app <-- solid.idp: Respond with Profile document
        deactivate solid.idp
        app -> app: Extract ""solid:oidcIssuer""
end group
else User Provides Issuer
    user o-> app: Provide Issuer URL
end

@enduml
